{"type": "article", "id": 26491, "title": "Stella McCartney 推出男装线，以及，Nike 又推出“耐克”鞋｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-05-06T10:23:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 13778, "name": "像素"}, {"id": 2355, "name": "眼镜"}, {"id": 6582, "name": "春夏"}, {"id": 7522, "name": "辞职"}, {"id": 26824, "name": "管理层"}, {"id": 18072, "name": "创意总监"}, {"id": 27282, "name": "蕾丝裙"}, {"id": 9470, "name": "Vans"}, {"id": 27283, "name": "Wood Wood"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 2211, "name": "Tod's"}, {"id": 20675, "name": "Avon"}, {"id": 3321, "name": "Stella McCartney"}, {"id": 21131, "name": "Self-Portrait"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}, {"id": 916, "name": "任天堂"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607132920B4yRMguCZcFz2N5s.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Ralph-Lauren-promotes-Valerie-Hermann-to-Global-President-Luxury,689907.html#.VyvjYoQrJQY\"><b>Ralph Lauren  管理层有系列变动</b></a>｜Ralph Lauren 的 CEO Stefan Larsson 近日正着手集团管理层的一系列变动，最显著的是 Valerie Hermann 的晋升，职位扩大到奢侈、女装和配饰的全球品牌总裁，新职位掌管旗下所有奢侈品牌，包括 Polo women’s、Lauren、Chaps、Denim &amp; Supply，男女鞋履、配饰和牛仔。Hermann 2014 加入公司担任奢侈系列总裁，此前在 Yves Saint Laurent  担任 CEO。此外，北美批发部门总裁 Kim Roy 离职，Roy 于 2003 年就加入公司。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Furla-CEO-Eraldo-Poletto-resigns,689987.html#.VyvmKIQrJQY\"><b>Furla CEO 辞职</b></a>｜Furla 近日宣布 CEO Eraldo Poletto 离职，六月底生效，据传之后他将加入 Salvatore Ferragamo，接替最近刚刚离职的 CEO Michele Norsa 的位置。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Tod-s-says-creative-director-Facchinetti-to-leave-company,689955.html#.VyvmNYQrJQY\"><b>Tod's 创意总监 Alessandra Facchinetti 离职</b></a>｜意大利奢侈品集团 Tod’s 周四宣布创意总监 Alessandra Facchinetti 离职，结束在集团三年的任期。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Cosmetics-maker-Avon-posts-surprise-loss,689951.html#.Vyvn8IQrJQY\"><b>Avon 季度亏损扩大</b></a>｜美容产品制造商雅芳 Avon 报道季度亏损扩大，在巴西及中国市场的需求进一步下跌导致收益减少了 16%，其中，南拉丁美洲的市场份额下跌幅度最大，销售额减少了 28%。三月，雅芳以 1.7 亿美元出售其 80% 的北美业务至 Cerberus Capital。净亏损扩大至 1.659 亿美元，去年同期为 1.473 亿。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Stella-McCartney-launches-men-s-line,689977.html#.VyvmLYQrJQY\"><b>Stella McCartney 推出男装线</b></a>｜Stella McCartney 将首次推出男装线，六月发布，首先在其巴黎的 showroom 进行展示，关于 Stella McCartney 要出男装线的传言已久，2011 年 10 月创立的 Stella McCartney，发展一段时间后并入开云旗下，过去几年，扩张到童装线、配饰、内衣等，泳装线也将在夏季六月至七月上市。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">一向很仙的 <a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/fashion/autumn-winter-2016/ready-to-wear/self-portrait-pre/full-length-photos/gallery/1547411\">Self-Portrait 发布了早秋系列</a>，各式各样的蕾丝裙、几何剪裁看起来很不错：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132901yQMDl4csAEI8Ledj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132901z1UmnLWh9oOIl4Xv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132902HnuPe1wk9dJvF3og.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132903JChZiuycrFT3DAEg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132904YFLQo75fV6UOwtn9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071329043Yh2jAUqPR4MXInt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132905HVLIP0Es3tfkiWBS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>重温童年像素时代的乐趣，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/nintendo-vans-collaboration\">Vans 近日最新的联名系列与日本任天堂（Nintendo ）合作</a>，Sk8-Hi, Old Skool, Authentic 和 Slip-On 经典鞋型，换上了超级马里奥、大金刚、Zelda 、红白机等为灵感的图案：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132905JXmpZOgtxkqr0SRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66706161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071329056lI1OxgvP3p2aRnr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66706161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132906NunJqlr7o0iEZv5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66706161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132907tGe9fN1d3AlDskCL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66706161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132907SEGaqpOKRWD2hc78.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66706161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132907yk27BSglx8v3ehdR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66706161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132908FNsHx683B5Xu7qR9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66706161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/thom-browne-2016-spring-summer-sunglasses\">Thom Browne  2016 春夏眼镜系列</a>，延续了品牌的美式美学，系列眼镜一向在日本手工制造，镜腿末端还有品牌标志性的红白蓝配色：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132908rCBuJIzP64vlfGQT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132909V6AP4MEeojslD8vH.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132909ImqNa4lrxWAEuzPR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132910TCsJpYz9jkmZGQ2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071329106p5EQIcstJwrGnBo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132911MpZsvoz5TeSnRirV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071329111uP28gL9wYMpCQyR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132913lL3TIrD4kRFnZJfQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/nike-tennis-classic-nai-ke-release-date\">Nike 又推出汉字“耐克”装饰的鞋</a>，这次采用的是网球鞋款，粒面皮革面料，5 月 5 日发售：</p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132913N2wvs7e4LuofkWjd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132914WicxAdR0ofXH65l2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6659919\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132914dxnBeLkDhsrpoIG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">哥本哈根品牌 Wood Wood 发布 2016 早秋牛仔系列<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/club-monaco-spring-2016-campaign/\"> </a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132915hNICB9XJEkVKUycd.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132915FCngjhxpavqBbfOG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060713291690hdfNElRGgKbCy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132916bRdBpHsytOVWSnTF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132917etAZqYzfNCHphFLb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/club-monaco-spring-2016-campaign/\">Club Monaco 发布 2016 春夏系列广告</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132917ogQxeyzOVtuMkLjr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071329189oixA7UbZjXTvhEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132918J5odjrlDzTu6WnAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132919uBG7r19LeKTQR8zw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}